<h2 id="email">Email Marketing: AWeber</h2>

Retail email marketing drives repeat purchases. Weekly newsletters with new arrivals, seasonal sales, exclusive offers for loyalty members, and automated post-purchase sequences all contribute directly to revenue.

AWeber works for retail chains because the deliverability is excellent -- your emails actually land in inboxes -- and the automation handles the sequences that drive repeat business without requiring a marketing team to manage.

<p><strong>Key retail email automations:</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>Welcome sequence for new customers (captured at POS or through WiFi portal)</li>
  <li>Post-purchase follow-up with product care and cross-sell suggestions</li>
  <li>Seasonal sale announcements segmented by purchase history</li>
  <li>Birthday and anniversary offers</li>
  <li>Re-engagement campaigns for lapsed customers</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Cost:</strong> Free to 500 subscribers, $20/mo for paid plans.</p>

